    "The effects are dual (Maqsood et al. 2020; Gu and Kurov 2020).",
    "On the one hand, Internet user comments and event information can have a substantial effect on the price of a stock.",
    "On the other hand, sudden fluctuations in stock price may prompt the development and transmission of relevant information (e.g., government viewpoints), which may then impact public perceptions of prospective investment strategies (Shomron and Weiser 2019; Jin et al. 2020).",
